    <item>
      <title>中国收紧对冲基金的监管，提高门槛和限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-tightens-rules-on-hedge-funds-with-higher-threshold-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国收紧了对冲基金的规则，提高了5.5万亿元人民币（7620亿美元）行业的最低资产门槛，同时对衍生品和杠杆的使用施加了限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-tightens-rules-on-hedge-funds-with-higher-threshold-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 04:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳伦德拉·莫迪在印度大选中投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-07/narendra-modi-votes-in-india-s-general-election-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在印度大选中投票。莫迪在家乡古吉拉特邦进行了第三阶段投票。印度马拉松选举的投票于4月19日开始，将持续到6月1日。获胜者将于6月4日宣布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-07/narendra-modi-votes-in-india-s-general-election-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 04:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
